# Assets Directory

Place all media files in this directory:

## Videos (≤ 25 MB each, MP4 format)
- hero.mp4 + hero-cover.jpg
- community-impact.mp4 + community-impact-cover.jpg
- programmes-esg.mp4 + programmes-esg-cover.jpg
- initiatives-masterclass.mp4 + initiatives-masterclass-cover.jpg

## Images (≤ 500 KB each, JPG/PNG format)
- logo-bsle.png
- favicon.png
- about-vision.jpg
- about-mission.jpg
- leadership-dr-rakhudu.jpg
- events-1.jpg
- events-2.jpg
- events-3.jpg
- events-4.jpg
- events-5.jpg
- contact-bg.jpg

## Notes:
- All video files should have a corresponding poster image (filename-cover.jpg)
- Use lazy loading for images in carousels
- Optimize all images before uploading
